# Safety Architecture Diagram

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Safety Layers
        MON[Health Monitor] --> WDG[Watchdog Timer]
        WDG --> FSM[Fail-Safe State Machine]
        FSM --> REC[Recovery Controller]
    end
    
    subgraph Monitored Systems
        NAV --> MON
        PWR --> MON
        THM[Thermal] --> MON
        COM --> MON
    end
    
    FSM --> ACT[Actuator Disable]
    REC --> REST[System Restart]
```
